Sergio Canavero says he is ready to be branded a Dr Frankenstein . 
  He plans to perform the first head transplant on a Russian with a rare muscle wasting disease . 
  Says he will carry out the operation in China if he is banned from doing so in the EU or former Soviet Union . 
  Claims the country which hosts the operation will be a 'world leader' like the US when it put a man on the Moon . 
  Claims it will take less than an hour to put his head on the body of a donor . 
  Claims he has no problem with wealthy tycoons using the procedure . 
  He hopes to operate on his first patient in less than a week . 
 